short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add the tinkercad assisstant to aid you with managing classrooms in tinkercad

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
TinkerCAD assissntant is your tool to manage your classrooms of tinkerCAD!
It allows you to download all your student's projects from the push of a button!
It gives you easy access tools to each project rather than going through menus!

It's now been rewritten to later be able to do loads more!
